# ============================================================
# Unused public assets
# ============================================================

## kenney_generic-items – komplett ungenutzt
frontend/public/kenney_generic-items/

## kenney_platformer-characters – alle Limbs-Ordner ungenutzt
frontend/public/kenney_platformer-characters/PNG/*/Limbs/

## kenney_platformer-characters – Root-Level Tilesheet-Dateien (z.B. zombie_tilesheet.png)
frontend/public/kenney_platformer-characters/PNG/*/*.png

## kenney_platformer-characters – aus Poses/ wird nur *_idle.png genutzt
frontend/public/kenney_platformer-characters/PNG/*/Poses/*
!frontend/public/kenney_platformer-characters/PNG/*/Poses/*_idle.png

## kenney_roguelike-indoors – nur roguelikeIndoor_transparent.png wird genutzt
frontend/public/kenney_roguelike-indoors/Kenney.url
frontend/public/kenney_roguelike-indoors/Patreon.url
frontend/public/kenney_roguelike-indoors/Preview.png
frontend/public/kenney_roguelike-indoors/Sample.png
frontend/public/kenney_roguelike-indoors/Tilesheets/roguelikeIndoor_magenta.png
frontend/public/kenney_roguelike-indoors/Tilesheets/tilesheetInfo.txt

## textures – nur floor_tile.png wird referenziert, alle anderen Ordner ungenutzt
frontend/public/textures/README.md
frontend/public/textures/PNG/
frontend/public/textures/Spritesheets/
frontend/public/textures/Vector/

